text: Just Roll with It is an American family comedy television series created by Adam Small and Trevor Moore. It aired on Disney Channel from June 14, 2019 to May 14, 2021. The series stars Ramon Reed, Kaylin Hayman, Suzi Barrett, Tobie Windham, and JC Currais.
